      .column.hideModuleDetails#moduleDetailsColumn
        .ui.top.attached.tabular.menu.moduleCompletionTabs
          a.active.item(data-tab='time_spent') Time Spent
          a.item(data-tab='timeline_actions') Timeline Actions
          a.item(data-tab='reflection') Reflection
        .ui.active.tab.bottom.attached.segment(data-tab='time_spent')
          .ui.stackable.two.column.grid.middle.aligned
            .column
              .ui.basic.segment.center.aligned(style="padding:0;")
                canvas#moduleTimePieChart(width="200" height="200" style="width:100%;height:100%;")
            .column
              .ui.basic.segment.left.aligned
                p 
                  | In the module&nbsp
                  span.emphasizedText.setModName (module name goes here)
                p 
                  | You spent&nbsp
                  span.emphasizedText#setTotalTime 0
                  | &nbsp minutes in total  
                  //- | (class average: 
                  //- span#setClassAvgTime ???
                  //- | &nbsp minutes)
                p 
                  | Learn:&nbsp
                  span.emphasizedText#setSection0Time 0 
                  | &nbspmin
                  br
                  | Practice:&nbsp
                  span.emphasizedText#setSection1Time 0  
                  | &nbspmin
                  br
                  | Explore:&nbsp
