              i.big.heart.icon
              | &nbsp&nbsp&nbspYou liked 
              span.emphasizedText#setLikeCount 0
              | &nbspposts
            p
              i.big.flag.icon
              | &nbsp&nbsp&nbspYou flagged 
              span.emphasizedText#setFlagCount 0
              | &nbspposts
            p
              i.big.reply.icon
              | &nbsp&nbsp&nbspYou wrote 
              span.emphasizedText#setReplyCount 0
              | &nbspreplies
        .ui.tab.bottom.attached.segment(data-tab='reflection')
          p 
            | In the module&nbsp
            span.emphasizedText.setModName (module name goes here)
          table.ui.celled.table
            thead
              tr 
                th 
                th Your Actions
                th Recommended Actions
            tbody
              tr.positive
                td Q1
                td I flagged the post
                td I flagged the post
              tr.negative
                td Q2
                td I liked the post
                td I flagged the post
              tr
                td Open Q1
                td This module is helpful...
                td NA
            
              
